1. GRANT OF LICENSE
-------------------

Subject to payment of the applicable license fee and continued compliance
with this agreement, the Licensor grants the Licensee a non-exclusive,
non-transferable, worldwide license to install and use Hour Terms on the
number of distinct Kirby installations permitted by the purchased license
tier:

  - "Freelancer" tier: one (1) Kirby installation
  - "Agency" tier: up to five (5) Kirby installations within a single
    organization, with up to five (5) named users across those installs
  - "Managed Install" tier: one (1) Kirby installation, operated on the
    Licensee's own hosting infrastructure with administrative access
    granted to the Licensor under the terms of a separate services
    agreement

A "Kirby installation" is a single Kirby content management system
instance running on a single primary domain. Staging and development
copies of the same instance do not consume additional license seats.


