7. PAYMENTS AND VAT
-------------------

Hour Terms license fees are processed through Stripe Payments. Joe
Gullo Digital is the seller of record for all transactions.

VAT is calculated and charged according to Dutch and EU tax law:

  - Customers in the Netherlands: VAT charged at the applicable
    Dutch rate
  - Customers in other EU countries (B2C): VAT charged at the
    customer's country rate, remitted via the EU One-Stop Shop scheme
  - EU business customers with a valid VAT identification number:
    reverse-charge mechanism applies (VAT not charged; customer
    accounts for VAT in their own jurisdiction)
  - Customers outside the EU: VAT not charged

Invoices showing all relevant tax information are issued automatically
after purchase and are available in the Licensee's buyer account at
hourterms.com.

